StringValues.16: The Kalindan of Palenqual, an Aun Tumerok relic. This missile weapon was given to the Aun xuta by spirits called the Deru. It is the embodiment of Marae Lassel's spirit - a single great totem for the island as a whole. Three Tumerok fetishes must be added to this weapon in order to use it, but choose carefully.
